299
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:15,800
Both of them.

300
00:17:17,950 --> 00:17:20,190
Xu Yiyi even told you a lot about my schedule.

301
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,040
Didn't she tell you

302
