Mr. Xia, how much can I get from the project?

305
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,950
Yiyi usually receives a bonus twice as much as mine.

306
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,470
She's just a common planner,

307
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,430
but I'm the person-in-charge of the project.

308
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:44,040
Besides, I'll have a quarterly bonus,
over-time pay and a year-end bonus.

309
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:49,680
Mr. Xia, it's my fault this time.

310
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,160
This suit is a gift from me to show my apology.

311
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:51,950
Don't thank me.

312
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,830
Are you an idiot?

313
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:08,040
Dongdong laughed at me

314
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:10,640
