316
00:18:13,310 --> 00:18:14,710
Shall I get a two-piece one?

317
00:18:15,110 --> 00:18:16,160
When did you start to

318
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:17,110
care about what they said?

319
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:19,110
I'm 24, okay?

320
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:21,040
If Chu Nan hears

321
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:21,800
their words,

322
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:22,830
it'll be embarrassing.

323
00:18:23,430 --> 00:18:25,070
Chu Nan? Will he join us?

324
00:18:25,590 --> 00:18:27,430
Yep. Everyone can take a partner, right?

325
00:18:28,430 --> 00:18:29,880
