326
00:18:29,950 --> 00:18:30,880
Are you sure you want to invite him?

327
00:18:31,430 --> 00:18:32,230
Actually, I'm not.

328
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,040
Since I said no,

329
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,680
I feel like everything is weird between us.

330
00:18:36,470 --> 00:18:38,520
Yiyi said I can take advantage of this chance

331
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:39,800
to foster our relationship.

332
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:41,710
Mr. Xia, what do you think of it?

333
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:45,280
