334
00:18:47,190 --> 00:18:48,400
I'm determined.

335
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:50,070
I have to do something.

336
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:52,560
I didn't hire you to do shopping.

337
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,640
Why are you angry again?

338
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:00,350
Add a piece of each kind of them.

339
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:05,190
Add some dried fish floss.

340
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,680
Now you can roll it.

341
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,070
Roll it up.

342
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:15,920
Mom, we're not going on a spring outing.

343
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:18,350
We're going to a five-star resort.

344
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:20,230
Three meals and even afternoon tea are available.

345
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,280
I didn't ask you to take it to the hotel.

346
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:25,280
It's for you to eat on the way.

347
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:26,640
Huh?

348
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:29,800
