Just eat!

353
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:41,070
No awkward silence can't be broken by food.

354
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:43,070
Silly girl, let me tell you.

355
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:46,470
When you're in a relationship,

356
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:49,830
you have to feed each other sometimes.

357
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:52,400
It helps give relationships a boost.

358
00:19:53,470 --> 00:19:56,110
