374
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:13,520
Hello? Amy.

375
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:18,950
What?

376
00:21:19,470 --> 00:21:20,590
Chu Nan, I'm sorry

377
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:22,000
