386
00:21:38,760 --> 00:21:39,760
See you in the resort.

387
00:21:39,830 --> 00:21:40,830
Safe trip.

388
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:41,350
Keep in contact.

389
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:43,310
Okay. See you later.

390
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:49,470
Morning!

391
00:21:49,590 --> 00:21:50,110
Xing Yun!

392
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:50,830
Morning!

393
00:21:52,040 --> 00:21:52,880
Here.

394
00:21:56,760 --> 00:21:57,950
Here is the last stop.

395
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,880
Morning, Mr. Xia.

396
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,430
Mr. Xia, actually, you could have saved money

397
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,470
on renting such a good coach.

398
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,880
We can go there by ourselves.

399
00:22:18,190 --> 00:22:19,920
Are you teaching me how I should spend my money?

400
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:38,470
Is the planning scheme finished?

401
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:40,680
Nah.

402
00:22:51,470 --> 00:22:52,280
Sorry, Mr. Xia.

403
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:54,070
I didn't sleep well last night.
It's not stained, right?

404
00:22:58,800 --> 00:22:59,640
That'd be great.

405
00:22:59,830 --> 00:23:00,950
I'd have to live on air this month

406
00:23:00,950 --> 00:23:02,430
