407
00:23:03,230 --> 00:23:04,000
What were you murmuring?

408
00:23:04,830 --> 00:23:05,470
Nothing.

409
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:07,760
When will we be there?

410
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:16,430
No awkward silence can't be broken by food.

411
00:23:20,950 --> 00:23:22,880
Mr. Xia.

412
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:26,230
The sushi is mine, right?

413
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,280
It explains why it tastes so bad.

414
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,800
I'm sorry about that.

415
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:46,280
This is the design drawing for the main cake.

416
00:23:46,280 --> 00:23:48,470
It has been modified as required.

417
00:23:49,230 --> 00:23:50,110
You have to

418
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:52,280
use strawberries imported from Japan.

419
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,590
Actually, it's not the best season

420
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:56,400
to have strawberries.

421
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:59,230
Besides, it'll be difficult for us

422
00:23:59,350 --> 00:24:01,400
