424
00:24:03,830 --> 00:24:05,280
Just tell the truth if you can't make it.

425
00:24:05,470 --> 00:24:06,710
Don't give such a lame excuse

426
00:24:06,710 --> 00:24:07,520
to fool us.

427
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:09,470
I'm telling you.

428
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,710
I don't care how it tastes

429
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:11,760
or if it's mature.

430
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:12,880
I just want imported strawberries.

431
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,470
Even if you don't care,

432
00:24:14,710 --> 00:24:16,640
I'd never let my clients

433
00:24:16,710 --> 00:24:18,950
get any dessert that tastes bad.

434
00:24:19,110 --> 00:24:20,880
I don't want to damage our reputation.

435
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:23,280
You even can't do such a simple thing.

436
00:24:23,470 --> 00:24:24,880
Honey, don't be angry.

437
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:27,110
Calm down.

438
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,280
You should be happy on our wedding anniversary.

439
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:30,920
Your makeup is messed up.

440
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:31,760
Why not go fix it?

441
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:33,400
I'll have a talk with Miss Shen.

442
00:24:34,760 --> 00:24:36,040
Imported strawberries only!

443
00:24:42,040 --> 00:24:43,520
Sorry, Miss Shen.

444
00:24:43,830 --> 00:24:45,680
My wife is short-tempered.

445
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,310
Please don't take it seriously.

446
00:24:49,190 --> 00:24:51,000
However, she said something right.

447
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:52,830
You're such a beautiful woman.

448
00:24:54,310 --> 00:24:56,800
Any cake will taste great

449
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:59,070
as long as it's made by you.

450
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:04,310
Mr. Lin, do you want to

451
00:25:04,310 --> 00:25:05,800
have a taste of the cake?

452
00:25:06,350 --> 00:25:08,310
I made it myself.

453
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,070
Yes, with pleasure!

454
00:25:12,430 --> 00:25:13,560
You're sensible.

455
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,230
Enjoy it.

456
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:27,830
We're already here.

457
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:29,590
It's okay. No hurry.

458
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:30,800
It doesn't matter if you come late.

459
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,230
Be safe.

460
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:38,880
