467
00:25:51,710 --> 00:25:53,040
He doesn't lack money.

468
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:59,230
Shen Qing, why are you here?

469
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,280
It's you.

470
00:26:00,350 --> 00:26:01,470
