488
00:26:51,950 --> 00:26:53,800
But the view nearby is great.

489
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:55,680
We can look around for a while.

490
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:57,880
Oh. There is

491
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:59,920
an eco-tourism attraction nearby.

492
00:27:00,230 --> 00:27:01,230
It's worth visiting.

493
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,070
Let's go.

494
00:27:02,190 --> 00:27:05,160
Mr. Xia, I'll stay.

495
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:06,160
My boyfriend hasn't arrived.

496
00:27:06,190 --> 00:27:07,190
I'll wait for him here.

497
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:11,110
Amy, Xing Yun doesn't want to
join the group activity.

498
00:27:11,190 --> 00:27:11,920
Her year-end bonus will be deducted.

499
00:27:12,430 --> 00:27:13,520
Year-end bonus? Mr. Xia.

500
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,520
It's about your year-end bonus. Let's go.

501
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:17,430
It's a large amount.

502
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:18,920
You're short of money. It's important to you.

503
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:20,680
Look!

504
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,430
Over there.

505
00:27:21,430 --> 00:27:22,470
There is a big fountain there.

506
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:25,160
When on earth will you stop it?

507
00:27:26,590 --> 00:27:29,110
Why are you so boring nowadays?

508
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:32,110
I'm in a good mood today.

509
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:37,070
