542
00:28:42,560 --> 00:28:43,000
Thank you!

543
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:46,280
One. Two. Three.

544
00:28:49,350 --> 00:28:50,000
Thank you!

545
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:52,230
It's great!

546
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:52,950
Xing Yun,

547
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:55,950
